dcterms:description: This dataset includes 255,668 distinct individuals who were tested for COVID-19 from March 22, 2020, to April 30, 2020. Each individual record has a test date. This dataset is used for the leakage quantification in COVID-19 contact tracing.
dcterms:title: COVID-19 dataset of tested individuals in Israel

dcterms:description: This dataset was collected on Taobao, a Chinese online shopping platform, and includes 25,029,435 ad display/click records concerning 827,009 ads and 1,061,768 individuals. The records were collected from May 6, 2017, to May 14, 2017. This dataset is used for leakage quantification to measure ad conversion revenue.
dcterms:title: Taobao dataset of ad display/click records
